skinparam HeadColor #00695C
skinparam ShadowColor #999999
skinparam linetype ortho

title AMS-AI: Release Roadmap\nVersion Strategy & Feature Timeline with SLAs & Metrics\n2026 - 2027 (Updated April 12, 2026)

timeline
