    section v0.1.0 Alpha (Q1-Q2 2026)
        Foundation Phase : crit, a1, 2026-01-15, 2026-03-31
        : Core Engine
        : Agent Registry
        : A2A Protocol Foundation
        : CLI Basics
        : SQLite Storage

    section v0.2.0 Alpha (Q2-Q3 2026)
        Orchestration : crit, a2, 2026-04-01, 2026-06-30
        : Workflow Builder
        : Execution Engine
        : Full A2A Protocol
        : REST API
        : PostgreSQL Migration
        : API Authentication

    section v0.3.0 Beta (Q3-Q4 2026)
        Applications : crit, a3, 2026-07-01, 2026-09-30
        : React Web App
        : Tauri Desktop App
        : Visual Workflow Canvas
        : WebSocket Real-time
        : JWT Authentication
        : RBAC System

    section v1.0.0 GA (Q4 2026)
        Production Ready : crit, a4, 2026-10-01, 2026-12-31
        : Enterprise Hardening
        : Horizontal Scaling
        : Prometheus/Grafana
        : Immutable Audit Logs
        : SSO (SAML/OIDC)
        : 99.9% SLA

    section v1.5.0 Enterprise+ (Q1-Q2 2027)
        Enterprise Features : crit, a5, 2027-01-01, 2027-06-30
        : Multi-Tenancy
        : Organization Hierarchy
        : Data Residency
        : SOC 2 Type II
        : Agent Marketplace
        : 99.95% SLA

    section v2.0.0 Next Gen (Q3-Q4 2027)
        Advanced AI : crit, a6, 2027-07-01, 2027-12-31
        : LLM Management
        : Prompt Engineering
        : Memory Systems
        : RAG Pipelines
        : MCP Integration
        : 99.99% SLA

@enduml
